f2f2\"|TBA ||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"| ''TVCA'' ||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"|A 1966 #2 ||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"| 1|| style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"|Sep 1965 || style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"|Colour || style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"|? ||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"| Neville Main\n|-\n\n| 13 || \"The Ordeals of Demeter\" || Gillian/John || TBA || ''TVC'' ||720 - 723 || 4|| 2 - 23 Oct 1965 || Colour || ? || Bill Mevin\n|-\n\n| 14 || \"Enter: The Go-Ray\" || Gillian/John || TBA || ''TVC'' ||724 - 727 || 4|| 30 Oct - 20 Nov 1965 || Colour || ? || Bill Mevin\n|-\n\n| 15 || \"The Frog People\" || Gillian/John || TBA || ''TVC'' ||728 - 731 || 4|| 27 Nov - 18 Dec 1965 || Colour || ? || Bill Mevin\n|-\n\n| 16 || \"A Christmas Story\" || Gillian/John || [[Santa Claus]] || ''TVC'' ||732 - 735 || 4|| 25 Dec 1965 - 15 Jan 1966 || Colour || ? || Bill Mevin\n|-\n\n| 17 || \"In Search of the Didus\" || Gillian/John || TBA || ''TVC'' ||736 - 739 || 4|| 22 Jan - 12 Feb 1966 || Colour || ? || Bill Mevin\n|-\n\n| 18 || \"Space Station Z-7\" || Gillian/John || TBA || ''TVC'' ||740 - 743 || 4|| 19 Feb - 12 Mar 1966 || Colour || ? || Bill Mevin\n|-\n\n| 19 || \"Plague of the Black Scorpi\" || Gillian/John || TBA || ''TVC'' ||744 - 747 || 4|| 19 Mar - 9 Apr 1966 || Colour || ? || Bill Mevin\n|-\n\n| 20 || \"The Trodos Tyranny\" || Gillian/John || Trods || ''TVC'' ||748 - 752 || 5|| 16 Apr - 14 May 1966 || Colour || Roger Noel Cook || John Canning\n|-\n\n| 21 || \"The Secret of Gemino\" || Gillian/John || TBA || ''TVC'' ||753 - 757 || 5|| 21 May - 18 Jun 1966 || Colour || Roger Noel Cook || John Canning\n|-\n\n|style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"| 22 ||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"| \"Guests of King Neptune\" || style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"|Gillian/John ||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"| TBA ||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"| ''TVCHS'' ||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"|HS 1966 #1 ||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"| 1||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"| May 1966 ||style=\"background:#f2f2f2\"| Duo ||style=\"back